1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,600
Science has a clearer story about the forgetting curve than social media ever will.

2
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:10,000
The forgetting curve shows how quickly we lose information over time.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,400
After just 20 minutes, we forget 40% of what we learn.

4
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:14,800
Surprised?

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:20,000
This was discovered by Hermann Ebbinghaus in the 1880s, revealing our brain's limits.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:22,800
But, spaced repetition can help combat this.

7
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:24,400
It’s all about timing!

8
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,000
Want to remember better?

9
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Follow for more science secrets that can change your learning!
